com.datastax.oss.dsbulk.executor.api.result

Interface ReadResult

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Result
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultReadResult

    public interface ReadResult
extends Result
    Represents one of the many results of a read operation.

    Each result encapsulates one Row returned by the execution of a read statement.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods Default Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Optional<Row> getRow()
      Returns the encapsulated Row object for this read result, if present.
      default void ifSuccess(Consumer<? super Row> consumer)
      If the result is a success, invoke the specified consumer with the returned Row, otherwise do nothing.
